{
  "stem": "27767.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the eighth day, they-- from-- they took us out to the field again in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from there, they took us to-- to the trains, to the rail station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they put us in-- it was raining, pouring, the whole day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after we were outside for about eight hours, we were all wet, all wet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- because we had this-- this clothing was like pajamas, very thin, what we had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we went-- they took us to the trains, the cattle wagons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they put us in the cattle wagons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they closed the doors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we said at that time, if we are not going to get pneumonia now, never.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were talking about this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you didn't where we are going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And once we saw from the train Krakow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So-- so we said-- so we are going east someplace, to-- to Poland someplace, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So-- and, finally, after two and a half or three days, we arrived to-- we saw the rail station Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So then they took us out from the trains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And with the SS behind us, with the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And actually, every three hours, you had the SS with their-- with the [NON-ENGLISH], with their-- and they took us to a camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We didn't know what is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was the Warsaw ghetto, we find out after that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It looked like-- we saw the big buildings, walls, because when the-- in '43, when they destroyed the ghetto, they bombed the ghetto with incendiary bombs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they did it-- the way the walls, the big walls, wouldn't be destroyed, because they wanted to have the bricks, and take them to Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when we arrived to that ghetto, it was-- we had barracks there.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
